{"tid":365544,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"日本推出少女汗味炸雞！","createTime":"2017-08-19T10:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T11:20:06.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7a2dc04e5ee52c33cbd0a89e7aa450c50824b8","tid":365544,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:30:33.000Z","msg":"講到汗味呢味嘢&hellip;&hellip;相信大家都會即刻聯想起喺酷熱天氣下，幾十人逼埋喺一卡港鐵車廂嘅濃烈氣味。尤其係汗腺特別發達、又啱啱行到身水身汗嘅男士，嗰陣味真係臭到想死！<br />\n<br />\n但如果有汗味嘅對象&hellip;&hellip;換咗做青春可愛又美麗嘅少女呢？情況又會唔會180度轉變呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/R6ixG1BHifi.kJuH2lm9ag--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTgwO2g9NDM1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/9d705a743574a7560f1ea2df498f5a0f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FR6ixG1BHifi.kJuH2lm9ag--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTgwO2g9NDM1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F9d705a743574a7560f1ea2df498f5a0f&h=fca9e488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本連鎖炸雞店「天下鳥ます」最近就推出咗一款期間限定嘅女子汗味炸雞，而且唔係隨隨便便喺街度揾個女仔返嚟，而係揾咗有最強地下偶像團體之稱嘅「假面女子」（仮面女子）合作！<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yCeaotJe3hPeiAURHSZhDw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NTA2/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/6aa62eace0ffe92b67dfd43526993c2f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FyCeaotJe3hPeiAURHSZhDw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NTA2%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F6aa62eace0ffe92b67dfd43526993c2f&h=e202c790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天下鳥ます店方表示，呢款炸雞係根據假面女子成員散發出嘅汗味而特&mdash;別&mdash;打&mdash;造。<br />\n<br />\n但少女嘅汗味到底係點嘅味道呢？原來就係由檸檬汁、芝士、鹽混合而成嘅醬汁，聽落其實都無咩問題吖，仲好似幾好食咁添～<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/x3MSAFuSJa2uDUoAhA1ezA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTgwO2g9NTgw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/fa0b91ad9f08beb50e0673ae1e06c03e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fx3MSAFuSJa2uDUoAhA1ezA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTgwO2g9NTgw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Ffa0b91ad9f08beb50e0673ae1e06c03e&h=23e40f2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ff58aaba841291954c24b6994b7b7368a8c492d","tid":365544,"uid":40072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:31:41.000Z","msg":"啫係嗅雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f04f9f7914c63d0a8c8ecf5bd70fcd5d27743e","tid":365544,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"麻友雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a118c4b2cdde000429d6678f6f2c1ad7403885","tid":365544,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:33:21.000Z","msg":"要麻友味"},{"pid":"d2df88b9d9bc80060b6a256acbd0a0a064cca09d","tid":365544,"uid":33443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:39:02.000Z","msg":"檸檬汁加芝士，又酸又臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7079c5d256f1d4ddc56965f2ee1c415c5961f9b6","tid":365544,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:46:53.000Z","msg":"有冇legging 味同黑c味？"},{"pid":"91110918f110ac7cc69a4d3a7946d62b28e2cbbe","tid":365544,"uid":43979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:50:22.000Z","msg":"有無閪水味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a4db4c597d862267ba350bad38a094c1677d39","tid":365544,"uid":38548,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T10:52:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啫係嗅雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gi